In [36]:
def floor_category(row): #    ,   apply       axis = 1
    floors_total = row['floors_total']
    floor = row['floor']
    if floor == 1:
        return ''
    elif floor == floors_total:
        return ''
    elif 1 < floor < floors_total:
        return ''
